  "texts": [
    "Tuning of these hyper-parameters was performed automatically within a 5-fold nested cross-validation loop.",
    "A random search with 25 iterations was used to select values for the hyperparameters in the inner loop and model performance was evaluated in the outer loop.",
    "In this way all model selection steps were repeated for every pair of training/test data.",
    "A list of the hyper-parameters that were tuned can be found in Supplementary Table S3 online.",
    "This table also shows the R packages used to implement each method."
  ],
